#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:38
msgid ""
"Hello translators!  Tutorial is meant to be a little funny at the start, "
"welcoming new players.  Please keep friendly fun feeling!  Any questions "
"email rusty@rustcorp.com.au!"
msgstr "Za prevodioce"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:39
msgid "Wesnoth Tutorial"
msgstr "Tutorijal Vesnotov"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:257
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:70
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:150
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:153
msgid "Konrad"
msgstr "Konrad"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:80
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:360
msgid "Quintain"
msgstr "drvenko"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:101
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:112
msgid "Delfador"
msgstr "Delfador"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:126
msgid ""
"You will learn the basics of:\n"
" movement\n"
" attacking\n"
" healing\n"
" recruiting"
msgstr ""
"Spoznaćeš sledeće veštine:\n"
" kretanje\n"
" napadanje\n"
" lečenje\n"
" najamljivanje"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:128
msgid "Destroy a fierce enemy"
msgstr "Smoždiš li ljutog suparnika"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:132
msgid "Get yourself killed"
msgstr "Nastradaš li"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:148
msgid "Who would you like to play?"
msgstr "U čije bi čizme da uskočiš?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:329
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:157
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:160
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:175
msgid "Li'sar"
msgstr "Lizara"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:189
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:197
msgid "*Welcome to Wesnoth!"
msgstr "*Dobro nam dođe u Vesnot!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:191
msgid ""
"\n"
"For this tutorial, you are playing Konrad. "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"U ovom tutorijalu vodićeš Konrada. "

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:192
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:200
msgid ""
"You are standing in the keep, and your mentor Delfador is on the East side "
"of the river."
msgstr ""
"Nalaziš se u zamku, a tvoj mentor Delfador čeka na istočnoj obali reke."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:194
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:202
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:224
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:230
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:240
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:245
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:382
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:387
msgid ""
"\n"
"*Left click or any key to continue..."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"*Levo klikni ili pritisni taster za dalje..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:199
msgid ""
"\n"
"For this tutorial, you are playing Li'sar. "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"U ovom tutorijalu vodićeš Lizaru. "

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:205
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:399
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:494
msgid "Left click on Konrad"
msgstr "Levo klikni na Konrada"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:206
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:400
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:495
msgid "Left click on Li'sar"
msgstr "Levo klikni na Lizaru"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:222
msgid ""
"*You have selected Konrad.\n"
"The places he could move to are highlighted."
msgstr ""
"*Odabra Konrada.\n"
"Konrad može dostignuti istaknuta polja."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:228
msgid ""
"*You have selected Li'sar.\n"
"The places she could move to are highlighted."
msgstr ""
"*Odabra Lizaru.\n"
"Lizara može dostignuti istaknuta polja."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:233
msgid "HERE"
msgstr "OVDE"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:238
msgid "Move Konrad next to Delfador, by clicking on the place marked 'HERE'."
msgstr "Pomeri Konrada do Delfadora klikom na polje označeno sa „OVDE“."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:243
msgid "Move Li'sar next to Delfador, by clicking on the place marked 'HERE'."
msgstr "Pomeri Lizaru do Delfadora klikom na polje označeno sa „OVDE“."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:249
msgid "Left click on tile labelled HERE"
msgstr "Levo klikni na polje gde piše OVDE"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:287
msgid ""
"*Oops!\n"
"You moved to the wrong place!  After this message, you can press 'u' to "
"Undo, then try again.\n"
"*Left click or any key to continue..."
msgstr ""
"*Ček'!\n"
"Ode na pogrešno mesto! Čim nestane ova poruka, možeš da pritisneš „u“ da "
"opozoveš potez, i potom uradiš kako ti rekoh.\n"
"*Levo klikni ili pritisni taster za dalje..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:310
msgid "Good morning Delfador!  Is it time to attack things?"
msgstr "Izvrsno jutro, Delfadore! Trenutak li je pravi, da napadnemo štogod?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:315
msgid "Um, well..."
msgstr "Eh, dete..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:320
msgid "Have you found an orc for me to fight, huh?  A troll?"
msgstr "Nađe li mi nekog orka za suparnika? Il' barem trola?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:325
msgid "Quiet!  I will summon an enemy for you..."
msgstr "Dosta! Dozvaću sad jednog protivnika tebi..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:365
msgid "... this quintain!"
msgstr "...ovog drvenka!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:370
msgid "A quintain?  You want me to pretend to fight a dummy??"
msgstr "Drvenka? Zar da se pretvaram kako se borim sa lutkom?!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:375
msgid ""
"Child, you have 32 hitpoints and a sword.    I'm fairly sure you'll win."
msgstr "Dete moje, imaš 32 udarpoena i mač. Cenim da ćeš sigurno pobediti."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:380
msgid ""
"To attack the quintain, you will first select the attacker (Konrad) and then "
"the target (the quintain).  You will see a description of the details of the "
"attack.  When you click OK, Konrad will attack."
msgstr ""
"Da napadneš, prvo izaberi napadača (Konrada), pa metu (drvenka). Dobićeš "
"potom sve detalje u vezi napada, i klikom na „U redu“ Konrad će napasti."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:385
msgid ""
"To attack the quintain, you will first select the attacker (Li'sar) and then "
"the target (the quintain).  You will see a description of the details of the "
"attack.  When you click OK, Li'sar will attack."
msgstr ""
"Da napadneš, prvo izaberi napadača (Konrada), pa metu (drvenka). Dobićeš "
"potom sve detalje u vezi napada, i klikom na „U redu“ Lizara će napasti."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:396
msgid "Click on the quintain to attack it"
msgstr "Klikni na drvenka da ga napadneš"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:429
msgid "Hey! This quintain fights back!"
msgstr "Svih mu...! Pa ovaj drvenko uzvraća!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:434
msgid "Hmm, maybe we should have started with a doll."
msgstr "[uzdah] Možda je trebalo da počnemo sa lutkicom."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:439
msgid "Should I retreat?"
msgstr "A da se ja povučem iz boja?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:444
msgid "Good idea!"
msgstr "Dobra zamisao!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Note: the tiny blue shield near Delfador shows that you will lose the game "
"if he is killed.  You will also lose the game if your leader (Konrad) is "
"killed."
msgstr ""
"Napomena: maleni plavi štit pored Delfadora kazuje da ćeš izgubiti nastrada "
"li on; jednako gubiš i ako tvoj vođ (Konrad) nastrada."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:452
msgid ""
"Note: the tiny blue shield near Delfador shows that you will lose the game "
"if he is killed.  You will also lose the game if your leader (Li'sar) is "
"killed."
msgstr ""
"Napomena: maleni plavi štit pored Delfadora kazuje da ćeš izgubiti nastrada "
"li on; jednako gubiš i ako tvoj vođ (Lizara) nastrada."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:461
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, you've used up your turn attacking the quintain.  The "
"quintain will now get a turn."
msgstr "Nažalost, tvoj potez prođe napadom na drvenka. Sada je red na drvenka."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:465
msgid "The DUMMY gets a turn?"
msgstr "LUTKA dobija potez?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:470
msgid ""
"Yes: it's a magical quintain.\n"
"Now, this quintain gets five chances to hit you, and if it hits every time, "
"you'll drop from $student_hp to $future_hp hit points.  Brace yourself!"
msgstr ""
"Nego kako — ovo je magični drvenko.\n"
"Obrati pažnju. Drvenko ima pet prilika da te udari; pogodi li te svaki put, "
"udarpoeni spašće ti sa $student_hp na $future_hp. Drž' se sad!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:472
msgid "Click on the End Turn button on the bottom right"
msgstr "Klikni na „Gotovo“ dole desno"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:484
msgid "Ouch!  I need to heal!  Only $student_hp hp left!"
msgstr "Ajao! Vidara, vidara! Udarpoeni mi odoše, ostade mi $student_hp!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:409
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:487
msgid "Village"
msgstr "Selo"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:491
msgid ""
"There is a village on the other side of the river.  Visiting villages is a "
"good idea, and ending your turn in one will heal you: you should retreat to "
"there."
msgstr ""
"Eno sela preko reke. Svratiti u selo je mudra odluka, ostaneš li tamo na "
"kraju poteza, izvidaće ti povrede. Stoga bolje trči tamo."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:503
msgid "Click on the village to move Konrad"
msgstr "Klikni na selo da pošalješ Konrada u nj"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:504
msgid "Click on the village to move Li'sar"
msgstr "Klikni na selo da pošalješ Lizaru u nj"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:521
msgid ""
"You now 'own' this village: you can see it flies your flag, and soon a '1' "
"will appear next to the house icon at the top of screen.  Villages give "
"gold: every turn you gain two gold, plus one for every village you own.\n"
"*Left click or any key to continue..."
msgstr ""
"Sada „poseduješ“ selo — nad njim se vijori barjak tvoj, a pojaviće se i „1“ "
"pored ikone kuće na vrhu ekrana. Sela daju zlato; u kesu ti se slivaju dva "
"zlatnika na potez, pa još po jedan za svako selo koje je tvoje.\n"
"*Levo klikni ili pritisni taster za dalje..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:523
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:621
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:651
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:728
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:777
msgid "Click on the End Turn button"
msgstr "Klikni na „Gotovo“"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:557
msgid ""
"You're about to be healed by 8 hitpoints.   But I think you're going to need "
"some help against that quintain."
msgstr ""
"Sada će ti izvidati 8 udarpoena. Ali razmišljah, ipak će ti trebati pomoć "
"protiv tog drvenka."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:562
msgid "I'll recruit some elves!"
msgstr "Pozvaću vilenjake dobre!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:934
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:565
msgid "Keep"
msgstr "zamak"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:569
msgid ""
"A splendid idea.  If you return to your keep, you can recruit two units.  "
"You have plenty of gold for that."
msgstr ""
"Razborito. Vratiš li se u zamak, možeš unajmiti dva saborca. Zlata ti "
"nedostati neće za taj čin, sigurno."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:573
msgid "Move Konrad to the keep"
msgstr "Pošalji Konrada u zamak"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:574
msgid "Move Li'sar to the keep"
msgstr "Pošalji Lizaru u zamak"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:593
msgid ""
"Whenever you're on a keep, you can recruit into castle tiles around it, by "
"right-clicking and selecting 'Recruit'.  This time you will only be given "
"one type of unit to choose: select it.\n"
"*Left click or any key to continue..."
msgstr ""
"Kad se zatekneš u zamku, možeš najamljivati u poljima njegovih zidina, tako "
"što ćeš desno kliknuti i izabrati „Unajmi“. Ovoga jutra, daće ti se samo "
"jedan tip jedinica na izbor, te ga izaberi.\n"
"*Levo klikni ili pritisni taster za dalje..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:596
msgid "Right click on one castle tile and select Recruit"
msgstr "Desno klikni na polje zamka i izaberi „Unajmi“"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:617
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:647
msgid ""
"These newly recruited units can do nothing this turn: you will control them "
"next turn.\n"
"Note: after this dialog, you can move the mouse over a unit to see a "
"description on the right of the screen.\n"
"*Left click or any key to continue..."
msgstr ""
"Novopristigle jedinice ne mogu nikud u ovom potezu, moraćeš sačekati "
"sledeći.\n"
"Napomena: posle ove poruke, možeš preći mišem preko jedinice da vidiš njen "
"opis desno na ekranu.\n"
"*Levo klikni ili pritisni taster za dalje..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:624
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:654
msgid "Right click on the other castle tile and Recruit another unit"
msgstr "Desno klikni na drugo polje zamka i unajmi još jednu jedinicu"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:667
msgid ""
"Hey, the quintain just healed by two hitpoints!  I'd better attack it at "
"once!"
msgstr ""
"Gle, drvenku se upravo obnoviše dva udarpoena! Bolje mi je udariti čim pre!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:672
msgid ""
"Yes, if a unit doesn't do anything for a turn, it will slowly heal.\n"
"But before you send your fighters against the quintain, you should know they "
"have two kinds of attack..."
msgstr ""
"Da, ne učini li ništa tokom poteza, jedinica će se malko zalečiti. Al' pre "
"nego pohitaš svojim borcima protiv drvenka, treba da znaš da oni umeju "
"udariti dvojako..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:676
msgid "I'll tell them to use the one which does most damage!"
msgstr "Reći ću im da udare tako da što više štete nanesu!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:680
msgid ""
"And which would that be?  The sword (5-4) or the bow (3-3)?  I guess you'll "
"find out..."
msgstr ""
"A kako bi to bilo, mačem (5-4) ili lukom (3-3)? Ubrzo ćeš i bez mene "
"spoznati..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:682
msgid "Left click on an Elvish Fighter"
msgstr "Levo klikni na vilin-borca"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:683
msgid "End your turn, then attack again."
msgstr "Završi svoj potez, a onda napadni ponovo."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:690
msgid "Left click on the Quintain to attack it."
msgstr "Levo klikni na drvenka da ga napadneš."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:719
msgid ""
"Your elf used a sword (5-4, or 5 damage, 4 attacks), which is a melee "
"attack, so the quintain defended with its melee attack (3-5).  The ranged "
"attack was safer."
msgstr ""
"Tvoj vilenjak upotrebi mač (5-4, znači 5 na štetu, u 4 udara), što beše "
"bliski napad, te se drvenko isto tako branio (3-5). Odstupni napad je bio "
"bezbedniji."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:726
msgid ""
"Your elf used a sword (5-4, or 5 damage, 4 attacks), which is a melee "
"attack, so the quintain defended with its melee attack (3-5).  The ranged "
"attack was safer.\n"
"End your turn, then attack again."
msgstr ""
"Tvoj vilenjak upotrebi mač (5-4, znači 5 na štetu, u 4 udara), što beše "
"bliski napad, te se drvenko isto tako braniše (3-5). Odstupni napad je bio "
"bezbedniji.\n"
"Okončaj svoj potez, te napadni ponovo."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:736
msgid ""
"Your elf used a sword (5-4, or 5 damage, 4 attacks), which is a melee "
"attack, so the quintain defended with its melee attack (3-5).\n"
"You should tell the other Elf to use the bow."
msgstr ""
"Tvoj vilenjak upotrebi mač (5-4, znači 5 na štetu, u 4 udara), što beše "
"bliski napad, te se drvenko isto tako braniše (3-5).\n"
"Treba da uputiš drugog vilenjaka da koristi luk."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:738
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:786
msgid "Attack with the other Elf"
msgstr "Napadni drugim vilenjakom"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:768
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:784
msgid ""
"Your elf used a bow, which is a ranged attack (3-3, or 3 damage, 3 "
"attacks).  The quintain has no ranged attack, only a melee attack, so it "
"could not defend itself."
msgstr ""
"Tvoj vilenjak upotrebi luk, što je odstupni napad (3-3, ili 3 na štetu, u 3 "
"udara). Drvenko nema odstupni napad, već samo bliski, pa se nije mogao "
"braniti."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:775
msgid ""
"Your elf used a bow, which is a ranged attack (3-3, or 3 damage, 3 "
"attacks).  The quintain has no ranged attack, only a melee attack, so it "
"could not defend itself.\n"
"End your turn, then attack again."
msgstr ""
"Tvoj vilenjak upotrebi luk, što je odstupni napad (3-3, ili 3 na štetu, u 3 "
"udara). Drvenko nema odstupni napad, već samo bliski, pa se nije mogao "
"braniti.\n"
"Okončaj svoj potez, te napadni ponovo."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:801
msgid "Keep attacking, with both elves, until the quintain is finished!"
msgstr "Nastavi da napadaš, obojicom vilenjaka, dok ne dovršiš drvenka!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:809
msgid "Maybe you should recruit another elf?"
msgstr "Možda da unajmiš još jednog vilenjaka?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:814
msgid ""
"Note:\n"
"You can right click on a unit to see a detailed Unit Description."
msgstr ""
"Napomena:\n"
"Desnim klikom na jedinicu možeš videti njen detaljan opis."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:829
msgid ""
"Note:\n"
"Remember to pull back wounded units into villages, and recruit more if you "
"need.  Take special care of units with the highest experience points (XP)."
msgstr ""
"Napomena:\n"
"Vodi računa da šalješ povređene jedinice u sela, i unajmiš nove kada ti "
"ustrebaju. Posebno čuvaj jedinice sa najviše iskustvenih poena (IP)."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:846
msgid ""
"Note:\n"
"These dummies only attack if you are a single tile away.  With care, you "
"should be able to kill them one at a time."
msgstr ""
"Napomena:\n"
"Ove lutke napadaju tek kada im se približiš na jedno polje. Malo pažnje, i "
"možeš ih sređivati jednu po jednu."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:857
msgid ""
"Note:\n"
"Each village you own can support a single unit for free.  After that, each "
"unit costs you one gold per turn."
msgstr ""
"Napomena:\n"
"Svako tvoje selo može izdržavati jednu jedinicu besplatno. Svaka jedinica "
"preko toga, koštaće te zlatnik po potezu."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:866
msgid ""
"Note:\n"
"When a unit gets enough experience (the experience bar is the smaller bar on "
"the right), it will go up a level.  Elvish Fighters have two options, and "
"you will get to choose which one you want."
msgstr ""
"Napomena:\n"
"Kada jedinica sakupi dovoljno iskustva (iskustvena traka je ona manja "
"desno), skočiće joj nivo. Vilin-borci imaju dve mogućnosti tada, i moći ćeš "
"da izabereš onu koju želiš."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:875
msgid ""
"Note:\n"
"Once you select a unit, you see percentages for different places: higher "
"means more defensible.  For example, defence is good in castles and "
"villages, bad inside rivers.  The dummies' attacks are magical, however, so "
"they have a 70% chance of hitting you wherever you stand."
msgstr ""
"Napomena:\n"
"Kada izabereš jedinicu, videćeš procente za različit teren; viši znači bolje "
"za odbranu. Na primer, odbrana je jaka u zamkovima i selima, loša usred "
"reke. Ali napad ovih lutki je magičan, tako da imaju 70% izgleda da te udare "
"gde god da stojiš."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:897
msgid "The quintain is dead, sirs, and I have gained more experience!"
msgstr "Drvenko je uništen, gospodo, a ja sam skupio više iskustva!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:901
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:905
msgid ""
"Yes, you gain more experience through battle, especially killing an "
"opponent: gain enough experience and you become more powerful."
msgstr ""
"Da, kroz bitke dobijaš iskustvo, a posebno kada ubiješ protivnika. "
"Sakupljajući iskustvo, moć ti raste."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:902
msgid ""
"Now Konrad, I will leave you with more dummies to practice on!  After that, "
"we have real work to do..."
msgstr ""
"Sada, Konrade, ostaviću te da odmeravaš snagu sa još lutaka! Nakon toga, "
"moramo se baciti na ozbiljnija dela..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:906
msgid ""
"Now Li'sar, I will leave you with more dummies to practice on!  After that, "
"we have real work to do..."
msgstr ""
"Sada, Lizara, ostaviću te da odmeravaš snagu sa još lutaka! Nakon toga, "
"moramo se baciti na ozbiljnija dela..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:953
msgid "Do you want to keep practicing?"
msgstr "Treba li ti još vežbanja?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:955
msgid "Yes, I'm still figuring it out."
msgstr "Da, još uvek isprobavam."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/1_Tutorial.cfg:958
msgid "No, I think I've got it."
msgstr "Ne, mislim da sam shvatio."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:26
msgid ""
"*Remember:\n"
"You can press 'u' to undo most things: useful to correct mistakes."
msgstr ""
"*Zapamti:\n"
"Pritiskom na „u“ možeš opozvati većinu stvari — korisno za ispravljanje "
"grešaka."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:38
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:48
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:61
msgid "*Galdrad"
msgstr "*Galdrad"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:73
msgid ""
", your new recruit, has two traits: strong and intelligent.  Strong means a "
"unit does more damage, and intelligent means it requires less experience to "
"advance a level."
msgstr ""
", tvoj novi borac, ima dve osobine: jačinu i oštroumnost. Jačina znači da "
"nanosi više štete, a oštroumnost da mu treba manje iskustva da dostigne "
"sledeći nivo."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Speaking.cfg:86
msgid ""
" has two traits: quick and resilient.  Quick means a unit can move one tile "
"further each turn, and resilient means it has more hitpoints."
msgstr ""
" ima dve osobine: brzinu i žilavost. Brzina znači da se može pomeriti jedno "
"polje više svaki potez, a žilavost da ima više udarpoena."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:25
msgid "Patch of forest"
msgstr "Ogranak šume"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Now put an unwounded unit, preferably a fighter, in that patch of forest on "
"the south-east of the island: a nice, defensible spot."
msgstr ""
"Sada postavi nepovređenu jedinicu, najbolje borca, u taj ogranak šume na "
"jugoistoku ostrva — mesto koje se lako može braniti."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:27
msgid "Can one unit survive against all those enemies?"
msgstr "Može li jedna jedinica preživeti pored svih tih neprijatelja?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:28
msgid ""
"With a little help, yes.  If you move your Shaman next to the defending "
"unit, it will heal it by 4 hitpoints per turn.  Just be careful not to "
"expose the Shaman to attack: it is fairly weak itself."
msgstr ""
"Uz malu pomoć, može. Ako postaviš vrača pored jedinice koja se brani, lečiće "
"je 4 udarpoena po potezu. Samo pazi da ne izložiš vrača napadu, jer je "
"prilično slab sam za sebe."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:29
msgid "Move a unit (fighter if possible) to the patch of forest"
msgstr "Pomeri jedinicu (borca ako je moguće) u taj ogranak šume"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:36
msgid ""
"Advance other units onto the island or to capture villages, then End Turn"
msgstr ""
"Pošalji druge jedinice na ostrvo ili u zauzimanje sela, pa onda „Gotovo“"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:131
msgid ""
"That unit is about one kill (8 experience points) away from gaining a "
"level!  Do not let it die!"
msgstr ""
"Toj jedinici fali još samo jedna pobeda (8 iskustvenih poena) da dostigne "
"sledeći nivo! Ne dozvoli da nastrada!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:183
msgid "I hope I get to retreat after this!"
msgstr "Nadam se da ću uspeti da se povučem posle ovoga!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:194
msgid "One lucky attack by an Orcish Grunt and I'm done for!"
msgstr "Posreći li se nekom orkovskom krmku, sa mnom je gotovo!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:205
msgid "Ouch!  I could use some healing in a village."
msgstr "Ajao! Dobro bi mi došlo vidanje u selu."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:231
msgid "I have $gold gold: enough to recruit!"
msgstr "Zlatnika imam $gold — dovoljno za najam!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:232
msgid "Yes, keep recruiting more units: I think you might need them!"
msgstr "Da, unajmi još jedinica, mislim da će ti trebati!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:243
msgid "Wesnoth Tutorial Part II"
msgstr "Tutorijal Vesnotov, deo drugi"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:268
msgid "Thrag"
msgstr "Thrag"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:285
msgid "Galdrad"
msgstr "Galdrad"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:296
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:335
msgid "Defeat the Orc Leader"
msgstr "Poraziš li vođa orkova"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:300
msgid "Death of Konrad"
msgstr "Nastrada li Konrad"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:304
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:343
msgid "Turns run out"
msgstr "Ostaneš li bez potezâ"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:339
msgid "Death of Li'sar"
msgstr "Nastrada li Lizara"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:378
msgid ""
"Ho Galdrad!  Has Delfador conjured something else to beat me with?  A flock "
"of scarecrows, perhaps?"
msgstr ""
"Ohoj, Galdrade! Da li je Delfador iznašao nešto da me nauči pameti? Jato "
"opakih gavrana ili takvo što?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:379
msgid "This is no game, Konrad! "
msgstr "Ovo nije igra, Konrade! "

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:380
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:381
msgid ""
"Orcs have encamped across the river.  This is elven country: we Elves are "
"fast and hard to hit in forests.  They are fools to enter here.  You must "
"defeat their leader, so they never bother us again.  I will advise you."
msgstr ""
"Orci su se ulogorili preko reke. Ovo je vilenjačka zemlja, i mi, vilenjaci, "
"brzi smo i teško nas je poraziti u šumama. Orci su budale ako misle da uđu "
"ovde. Moraš pobediti njihovog vođa, da nas više nikada ne bi smetali. Ja ću "
"te savetovati."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:380
msgid "This is no game, Li'sar! "
msgstr "Ovo nije igra, Lizara! "

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:382
msgid "What should I do?"
msgstr "Šta treba da radim?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:387
msgid ""
"First, we will have to deal with the Orcish Grunt stationed in the middle of "
"the river.  He should be little trouble."
msgstr ""
"Prvo treba da se obračunamo sa onim orkovskim groktašem, tamo na sredini "
"reke. Nikakav problem, mišljenja sam."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:388
msgid ""
"By then, their leader will have recruited units to send against us, and the "
"real fight will begin."
msgstr ""
"Ali do tada, njihov vođ će već sazvati jedinice i poslati ih na nas, i prava "
"bitka će započeti."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:389
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:390
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:391
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:392
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:393
msgid "SHALLOW"
msgstr "PLITKO"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:394
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:395
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:396
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:397
msgid "DEEP"
msgstr "DUBOKO"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:399
msgid ""
"See this dark blue water: it is too deep for either side to cross.  They "
"could slowly wade through that narrow band of shallow lighter-blue water in "
"the east, but we would stand on the shore and force them to fight us from "
"the water, where they are exposed and we are protected by the forest."
msgstr ""
"Smotri tamno plavu vodu; previše duboka bilo za nas, bilo za njih. Mogli bi "
"sporo da gaze preko onog tankog pojasa plitke, svetlo plave vode na istoku, "
"ali bismo ih mi čekali na obali. Morali bi tada da se bore iz vode, gde su "
"izloženi, a mi iz zaklona šume nam mile."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:410
msgid ""
"The more likely attack, then, is across the bridge.  That middle island is "
"the key: it has a village, for healing injured units, and forest in which we "
"fight so well."
msgstr ""
"Stoga je mogućnije da pohitaju k nama preko mosta. Ostvo u sredini mora biti "
"naš oslonac — ima selo za vidanje naših junaka, i šumu u kojoj se tako dobro "
"borimo."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:415
msgid ""
"To start, we will need some units:\n"
"Two Elvish Fighters\n"
"Two Elvish Archers\n"
"One Elvish Shaman"
msgstr ""
"Počnimo onda, okupljanjem nekoliko jedinica:\n"
" dva vilin-borca\n"
" dva vilin-strelca\n"
" jedan vilin-vrač"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:482
msgid ""
"During your tutorial, $recall_name1 gained $recall_xp1 experience points, "
"and $recall_name2 gained $recall_xp2.  You should recall them now so they "
"can gain more experience, rather than recruiting new ones."
msgstr ""
"Tokom tutorijala do sada, $recall_name1 sakupi $recall_xp1 iskustva, a "
"$recall_name2 sakupi $recall_xp2. Bolje ih sazovi pre najamljivanja novih "
"jedinica, tako da mogu steći još iskustva."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:486
msgid ""
"During your tutorial, $recall_name1 gained $recall_xp1 experience points.  "
"You should recall that unit now, and recruit a second one (which is cheaper "
"than recalling, anyway)."
msgstr ""
"Tokom tutorijala do sada, $recall_name1 sakupi $recall_xp1 iskustva. Bolje "
"sazovi sada tu jedinicu, a unajmi još jednu (unajmljivanje je ionako "
"jeftinije od sazivanja starih saboraca)."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:489
msgid "RECALL $recall_name1"
msgstr "SAZOVI $recall_name1"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:490
msgid "Right click on the tile south of you and recall $recall_name1"
msgstr "Desno klikni na polje južno od sebe i sazovi $recall_name1"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:499
msgid ""
"If any Elvish Fighters from your last battle had experience, we would recall "
"them: as they don't, it's cheaper to recruit new ones.  So recruit an Elvish "
"Fighter."
msgstr ""
"Da je neki od vilin-boraca iz poslednje bitke stekao iskustva, trebalo bi da "
"ga sazovemo nazad. Ali pošto nije, jeftinije je unajmiti nove. Stoga unajmi "
"jednog vilin-borca."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:502
msgid ""
"If you had any experienced units alive from your last battle we would recall "
"them, instead we must recruit a new Elvish Fighter."
msgstr ""
"Da ti je ijedna iskusna jedinica ostala živa u poslednjoj bici, sazvali "
"bismo je, ali pošto nije, moramo unajmiti novog vilin-borca."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:505
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:782
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:825
msgid "Elvish Fighter"
msgstr "Vilin-borac"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:506
msgid "Right click on the tile south of you and recruit an Elvish Fighter"
msgstr "Desno klikni na polje južno od sebe i unajmi vilin-borca."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:540
msgid "No!  I said recruit an Elvish SHAMAN!  Now try again..."
msgstr "Šta bi?! Rekoh unajmi vilin-VRAČA! Hajde ponovo..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:546
msgid ""
"The Shaman is a fairly weak unit, but has the ability to heal units around "
"it.  It also has a special attack which slows enemies, halving the damage "
"they do!"
msgstr ""
"Vrač je relativno slaba jedinica, ali ume da leči jedinice u svojoj blizini. "
"Takođe poznaje tehniku napada kojom usporava neprijatelje, prepolovljavajući "
"štetu koju nanose!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:547
msgid "So, should I end my turn now?"
msgstr "Pa, da završim sada svoj potez?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:549
msgid ""
"It's true, none of your recruited units can move, but you still can.  Your "
"five units cost you 5 gold, leaving you 3 gold pieces poorer per turn.  You "
"need more income."
msgstr ""
"U pravu si, nijedna od unajmljenih jedinica ne može da se pomeri, ali ti "
"možeš. Tvojih pet jedinica košta 5 zlatnika, ostavljajući te sa 3 zlatnika "
"manje po potezu. Treba ti još prihoda."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:550
msgid "Move Konrad to capture a village"
msgstr "Pomeri Konrada da zauzme selo"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:551
msgid "Move Li'sar to capture a village"
msgstr "Pomeri Lizaru da zauzme selo"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:570
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:615
msgid "No!  I said recruit an Elvish ARCHER!  Now try again..."
msgstr "Ne tako! Rekoh unajmi vilin-STRELCA! Hajde ponovo polako..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:579
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:591
msgid "Eowynial"
msgstr "Eovinjal"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:595
msgid "Shaman"
msgstr "vrač"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:596
msgid "Recruit an Elvish Shaman to your north"
msgstr "Unajmi vilin-vrača u polju severno"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:624
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:635
msgid "Elriend"
msgstr "Elrijend"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:662
msgid "No!  I said RECALL $recall_name2|!  Now try again..."
msgstr "Čekaj! Rekoh SAZOVI $recall_name2|! Hajde iz početka..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:667
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:709
msgid "Archer #1"
msgstr "strelac #1"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:668
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:710
msgid "Archer #2"
msgstr "strelac #2"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:669
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:711
msgid "Recruit two Elvish Archers in tiles to your west"
msgstr "Unajmi dva vilin-strelca u poljima zapadno od sebe"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:685
msgid "No!  I said recruit an Elvish FIGHTER!  Now try again..."
msgstr "Loše! Rekoh unajmi vilin-BORCA! Hajde sad pažljivije..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:695
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:706
msgid "Golir"
msgstr "Golir"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:757
msgid "No!  I said recall $recall_name1, not $recall_name2|!  Now try again..."
msgstr ""
"Šta je to?! Rekoh sazovi $recall_name1, a ne $recall_name2|! Ponovi sad kako "
"treba..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:761
msgid ""
"No!  I said RECALL $recall_name1 from the last battle, not recruit a new "
"$recruit.type|!  Now try again..."
msgstr ""
"Ne valja! Rekoh SAZOVI $recall_name1 iz prethodne bitke, a ne da unajmiš "
"$recruit.type|! Ponovi to pravilno..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:778
msgid "Right click on the tile south-east of you and recall $recall_name2"
msgstr "Desno klikni na polje jugoistočno od sebe i sazovi $recall_name2"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:779
msgid "RECALL $recall_name2"
msgstr "SAZOVI $recall_name2"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:783
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:826
msgid "Right click on the tile south-east of you and recruit an Elvish Fighter"
msgstr "Desno klikni na polje jugoistočno od sebe i unajmi vilin-borca"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:799
msgid "$recruit.type|?  I said RECRUIT a new ELVISH FIGHTER.  Now try again..."
msgstr "$recruit.type|? Rekoh UNAJMI novog VILIN-BORCA. Ponovi to ispravno..."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:813
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:824
msgid "Elindel"
msgstr "Elindel"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:852
msgid "You've learned well, Konrad! "
msgstr "Dobro si naučio, Konrade! "

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:853
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:855
msgid ""
"The village supports one unit, and pays one gold per turn: you're only "
"losing 1 gold per turn now."
msgstr ""
"Selo podržava jednu jedinicu i plaća jedan zlatnik po potezu. Tako sada "
"gubiš samo 1 zlatnik po potezu."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:854
msgid "You've learned well, Li'sar! "
msgstr "Dobro si naučila, Lizara! "

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:856
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:976
msgid "End your turn"
msgstr "Završi potez"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:862
msgid ""
"You've captured all the villages around the keep, but stay near so you can "
"recruit more units."
msgstr ""
"Sva sela oko zamka su zauzeta, ali ostani u blizini radi najamljivanja novih "
"jedinica."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:877
msgid ""
"You should leave the villages near your keep for Konrad to capture, as he "
"needs to stay nearby to recruit more units anyway."
msgstr ""
"Treba da ostaviš sela blizu zamka Konradu da ih zauzme, pošto on ionako mora "
"ostati u blizini zamka radi najma novih jedinica."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:878
msgid ""
"You should leave the villages near your keep for Li'sar to capture, as she "
"needs to stay nearby to recruit more units anyway."
msgstr ""
"Treba da ostaviš sela blizu zamka Lizari da ih zauzme, pošto ona ionako mora "
"ostati u blizini zamka radi najma novih jedinica."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:884
msgid "Orcs have no ranged attack, so use your archers against it."
msgstr "Orci nemaju odstupni napad, zato koristi svoje strelce protiv njih."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:886
msgid ""
"Attack the Orc with an Archer (move mouse over units to see description on "
"right)"
msgstr ""
"Napadni orka strelcem (pomeri miš preko jedinice da bi video njen opis desno)"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:894
msgid ""
"Excellent.  Elves are well protected in the forest: there's only a 30% "
"chance of hitting an Elven Archer when it's in forest."
msgstr ""
"Izvrsno. Vilenjaci su dobro zaštićeni u šumi. Samo je 30% izgleda da neko "
"pogodi vilin-strelca dok je u šumi."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:903
msgid ""
"It's very dangerous to stand in water when there are enemies about!  Your "
"unit would have an 80% chance of being hit when the Orc counter-attacks!  "
"Cancel!"
msgstr ""
"Veoma je opasno gaziti kroz vodu kada u okolini ima neprijatelja! Izgledi su "
"80% da tvoja jedinica bude pogođena kada ork uzvrati napad! Bolje odustani!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:909
msgid "Attack the Orc with the other Archer"
msgstr "Napadni orka drugim strelcem"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:921
msgid "Fighter to Here"
msgstr "Borac ovde"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:922
msgid ""
"Your other units cannot reach that Orc this turn.  Send a Fighter to that "
"village to the far east: that will take two turns."
msgstr ""
"Tvoje ostale jedinice ne mogu dopreti do tog orka u ovom potezu. Pošalji "
"borca u ono selo skroz na istoku, za to će mu trebati dva poteza."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:923
msgid ""
"You can make a unit keep moving for multiple turns: select the unit, then "
"click on the target.  You will see (2) if it will take two turns to reach it."
msgstr ""
"Možeš odrediti jedinici da se kreće tokom više poteza: izaberi je, pa klikni "
"na cilj. Videćeš (2) ako jedinici treba dva poteza da dostigne to mesto."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:924
msgid "Tell a Fighter to move to the far east village"
msgstr "Pošalji borca u selo skroz na istoku"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:935
msgid ""
"Send the other Fighter and the Shaman south so they can attack next turn, "
"then return to the keep to recruit more units!"
msgstr ""
"Pošalji drugog borca i vrača na jug, da bi mogli da napadnu u sledećem "
"potezu, a onda se vrati u zamak da unajmiš još jedinica!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:936
msgid "Move Fighter and Shaman south, then return Konrad to the Keep"
msgstr "Pošalji borca i vrača na jug, a onda vrati Konrada u zamak"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:937
msgid "Move Fighter and Shaman south, then return Li'sar to the Keep"
msgstr "Pošalji borca i vrača na jug, a onda vrati Lizaru u zamak"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:947
msgid "Recruit another Archer and a Fighter"
msgstr "Unajmi još jednog strelca i borca"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:962
msgid "I have no more money to recruit!"
msgstr "Nemam više novaca za najam!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:963
msgid "This is often a problem, which is why owning villages is important."
msgstr "Ovo je česta nevolja, i baš zato je bitno zauzimati sela."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:964
msgid "Move Konrad to another (unowned) village"
msgstr "Pomeri Konrada na drugo (nezaposeto) selo"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:965
msgid "Move Li'sar to another (unowned) village"
msgstr "Pomeri Lizaru na drugo (nezaposeto) selo "

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:990
msgid ""
"The Orc is blocking the bridge!  We must occupy that island before the wolf "
"riders reach it."
msgstr ""
"Ork blokira most! Moramo preuzeti to ostrvo pre nego što vukosedlaši "
"pristignu na nj."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:991
msgid "Can't our units just move around him?"
msgstr "Ne mogu li naše jedinice samo da ga zaobiđu?"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:994
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:995
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:996
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:997
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:998
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:999
msgid "ZoC"
msgstr "NAPOJ"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1002
msgid ""
"No: once you move close to an enemy unit, you are in it's 'Zone of Control', "
"and cannot move further that turn.\n"
"To move your troops onto that island without wading slowly through the "
"water, you'll have to kill him."
msgstr ""
"Ne — kada se približiš blizu neprijatelju, ušao si u njegov „nadzorni pojas“ "
"i ne možeš se više pomeriti u tom potezu.\n"
"Da bi pomerio svoje snage na to ostrvo bez sporog gaženja vodom, moraćeš da "
"ubiješ neprijatelja."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1003
msgid "Attack the Orc with an Archer"
msgstr "Napadni orka strelcem"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1025
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1037
msgid "Advance other units and capture villages, then End Turn"
msgstr "Pošalji napred druge jedinice i zauzimaj sela, pa „Gotovo“"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1029
msgid ""
"No other units can reach that Orc: I hope my archer survives its counter-"
"attack!  I'd better grab more villages, and move everyone closer for next "
"turn."
msgstr ""
"Nijedna druga jedinica ne može da dopre do tog orka — nadam se da će moj "
"strelac preživeti njegov protivnapad! Bolje da zgrabim još sela i približim "
"druge u sledećem potezu."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1030
msgid ""
"Yes.  If your Shaman stands just behind that unit on the bridge, it will "
"heal it at the beginning of next turn, too."
msgstr ""
"Da. Ukoliko vrač stoji odmah iza te jedinice na mostu, zalečiće i nju na "
"početku sledećeg poteza."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1031
msgid "Move Shaman onto bridge to stand behind unit"
msgstr "Pomeri vrača na most tačno iza odbrambene jedinice"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1077
msgid ""
"Be careful: if you stand on the bridge you are exposed to attack from "
"multiple directions!"
msgstr "Ali pazi, kada stojiš na mostu, napad može stići sa više strana!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1090
msgid ""
"It's very dangerous to stand in water when there are enemies about!  Your "
"unit would have an 80% chance of being hit!  Cancel, and wait for them to "
"attack you!"
msgstr ""
"Veoma je opasno gaziti kroz vodu kada u okolini ima neprijatelja! Izgledi su "
"80% da tvoja jedinica bude pogođena! Bolje odustani, i čekaj da oni napadnu "
"tebe!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1100
msgid ""
"Don't forget about your fighter in the east: you can move him south to that "
"last village near the channel."
msgstr ""
"Ne zaboravi onog borca na istoku. Možeš ga pomeriti južno do poslednjeg "
"sela, blizu kanala."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1107
msgid ""
"We need to take that village, otherwise they will take it next turn!  Move "
"your wounded unit to take it so it can heal, then kill that Orc!"
msgstr ""
"Moramo da zauzmemo to selo, inače će ga oni uzeti u sledećem potezu! Zauzmi "
"selo povređenom jedinicom, gde može i da se leči, pa onda sredi tog orka!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1120
msgid ""
"Careful!  It is now nighttime.  Orcs are chaotic: their attacks are 25% "
"stronger at night, 25% weaker in the day.  You are lawful: stronger by day.  "
"Elves are neutral: we are unaffected by night and day."
msgstr ""
"Oprezno! Noć se spustila, a orci su stvorenja Haosa. Njihovi napadi su 25% "
"jači noću, a 25% slabiji danju. Ti si zakonska rasa, jači danju. Vilenjaci "
"su neutralni, nama su i noć i dan jednaki."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1121
msgid ""
"After this dialog, hold the mouse over the image below the map on the right, "
"to see a description of the time of day."
msgstr ""
"Posle ove poruke, drži miš preko sličice iznad mape na desnoj strani, da bi "
"video koje je doba dana."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1128
msgid ""
"Remember to retreat your wounded units to villages.  Healers can only heal 4 "
"hitpoints at a time, villages can heal 8 (the maximum for any unit)."
msgstr ""
"Vodi računa da povlačiš povređene jedinice u sela. Vidari mogu lečiti samo 4 "
"udarpoena po potezu, a sela 8 (najviše za bilo koju jedinicu)."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1135
msgid "Defend here"
msgstr "Brani ovo ovde"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1136
msgid ""
"Beware those Orcs crossing the river!  If they get into the forest they'll "
"be hard to dislodge!"
msgstr ""
"Čuvaj se tih orkova što prelaze reku! Uđu li u šumu, biće ih se teško "
"otarasiti!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1143
msgid ""
"You can make sure you've used all your units for this turn: press 'n' for "
"the next unit, SPACE to indicate it's finished.\n"
"When 'n' no longer selects a new unit, you can end your turn."
msgstr ""
"Možeš se uveriti da si upotrebio sve jedinice u ovom potezu: pritisni „n“ za "
"sledeću jedinicu, a RAZMAK da joj odrediš mirovanje.\n"
"Kada „n“ više ne bira sledeću jedinicu, možeš okončati potez."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1148
msgid "You only need to defeat the leader to win: see Main Menu->Objectives."
msgstr ""
"Treba da poraziš samo vođa da bi pobedio: vidi Glavni Meni->Ciljevi "
"scenarija."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1153
msgid ""
"Remember to recruit more troops as you need them: Archers are particularly "
"effective against Grunts, Wolf Riders and their leader."
msgstr ""
"Pazi da unajmljuješ još snaga kada ti zatrebaju. Strelci su posebno "
"delotvorni protiv groktaša, vukosedlaša i njihovog vođa."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1171
msgid ""
"Stay near the keep: you need to be on a keep to recruit more units, and I "
"doubt the Orc leader will let you use his!"
msgstr ""
"Ostani blizu zamka; samo tu možeš unajmiti nove snage, jer čisto sumnjam da "
"će ti vođ orkova dati svoje pod komandu!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1185
msgid ""
"Their leader has moved into that village!  He's not as stupid as I thought: "
"it heals him each turn and provides good defense."
msgstr ""
"Njihov vođ je ušao u to selo! Nije tako glup kao što sam mislio, ovako se "
"leči svaki potez i u dobrom je zaklonu."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1196
msgid ""
"That unit has captured our village!  You'd better get him out: it heals him "
"each turn and provides good defense."
msgstr ""
"Ta jedinica je zauzela naše selo! Bolje ga isteraj odatle, jer se leči svaki "
"potez i u dobrom je zaklonu."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1208
msgid ""
"Using me to attack is risky!  I can slow the opponent with my ranged attack, "
"but I hope you have a plan if I miss!"
msgstr ""
"Rizično je koristiti mene u napadu! Mogu usporiti protivnika svojim "
"odstupnim napadom, ali se nadam da imaš rezervni plan ako promašim!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1244
#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1260
msgid ""
"You are close to killing their leader!  The unit which finishes him will "
"gain 16 experience points, because he is level 2.  Choose your unit "
"carefully!"
msgstr ""
"Samo što im nisi sredio vođa! Jedinica koja ga dovrši dobija 16 iskustvenih "
"poena, jer je on nivo 2. Biraj jedinicu pažljivo!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1301
msgid ""
"We will miss $deadguy.user_description|, and he had $deadguy.experience "
"experience points, meaning he would have advanced to level 2 soon."
msgstr ""
"Nedostajaće nam $deadguy.user_description|, a i imaše $deadguy.experience "
"iskustvenih poena, što znači da mu je malo nedostajalo do nivoa 2."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1310
msgid ""
"We will miss $deadguy.user_description|, but better than one of our "
"experienced troops dying!"
msgstr ""
"Nedostajaće nam $deadguy.user_description|, ali bolje tako, nego da nastrada "
"neka od naših iskusnijih jedinica!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1323
msgid ""
"Losing a healer hurts all the troops!  Keep them out of the enemy's reach!"
msgstr ""
"Gubitak vidara šteti svim našim snagama! Čuvaj ga van dohvata neprijatelja!"

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1324
msgid ""
"You can see where an enemy could reach by moving the mouse over them.  You "
"can see all the possible enemy moves at once with 'Show Enemy Moves' from "
"the 'Actions' menu."
msgstr ""
"Možeš da vidiš kuda bi neprijatelj mogao stići, postavljanjem miša preko "
"njega. Možeš videti sve moguće poteze neprijatelja odjednom, pomoću „Prikaži "
"protivničke poteze“ u meniju „Radnje“."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1328
msgid ""
"Level 2 units are powerful, but not invulnerable!  Goodbye, $deadguy."
"user_description|."
msgstr ""
"Jedinice nivoa 2 su moćne, ali ne i neranjive! Zbogom, $deadguy."
"user_description|."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1343
msgid ""
"Beware the leader: he can do 36 hitpoints damage at night!  Attack with many "
"units at once, during the day."
msgstr ""
"Čuvaj se vođa — može da nanese 36 poena štete tokom noći! Napadni sa mnogo "
"jedinica istovremeno, i u toku dana."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1356
msgid ""
"Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I always have a 60% chance of hitting with my bow, and 9 hitpoints damage on "
"each of the four attacks.  Use me to dislodge hard-to-hit units."
msgstr ""
"Napredovanje nivoa me je potpuno zacelilo!\n"
"Uvek imam 60% izgleda da pogodim svojim lukom, i 9 udarpoena štete za svaki "
"od četiri napada. Koristi me da izglaviš teško uhvatljive jedinice."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1368
msgid ""
"Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I am good with both bow and sword, but I have a special ability: ambush.  I "
"can hide in forests, and enemies can only see me if they are right next to "
"me."
msgstr ""
"Napredovanje nivoa me je potpuno zacelilo!\n"
"Dobar sam i s lukom i s mačem, ali imam i posebnu sposobnost: zasedu. Mogu "
"se kriti u šumi tako da me neprijatelj može videti samo ako stupi odmah do "
"mene."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1380
msgid ""
"Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I am good with both bow and sword, but I have a special ability: "
"leadership.  Level 1 units around me do 25% more damage, so position me "
"carefully."
msgstr ""
"Napredovanje nivoa me je potpuno zacelilo!\n"
"Dobar sam i s lukom i s mačem, ali imam i posebnu sposobnost: vođstvo. "
"Jedinice nivoa 1 u mojoj blizini nanose 25% više štete, zato me pažljivo "
"rasporedi."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1393
msgid ""
"Advancing a level has fully healed me!\n"
"I am particularly good with the sword: four attacks doing 8 damage each."
msgstr ""
"Napredovanje nivoa me je potpuno zacelilo!\n"
"Posebno sam dobar s mačem: četiri napada, svaki nanosi 8 poena štete."

#: data/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1560
msgid "You took too long, we'll never be rid of these Orcs!"
msgstr "Dugo ti je trebalo, sada se nikada nećemo osloboditi ovih orkova!"
